data.description: Welcome to your new home at 172 Easy Pines Way! Immerse yourself in the vibrant active lifestyle of Marietta Square, just a short walk away. Experience the lifestyle you have been searching for as you enjoy all that living near the Square has to offer. Holiday festivals, outdoor concerts, exploring the Saturday Farmer's Market, shopping and relishing in dining and entertainment options. Outdoor recreation at Kennesaw Mountain National Park is minutes away.  Hurry to this stunning 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom, END UNIT Townhome that is loaded with upgrades and high-end finishes. This unique LOCK and LEAVE property is situated in the desirable MANGET subdivision. The gourmet chef's kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, including a wine cooler, walk in pantry and is open to the great room. The generous island is perfect for casual entertaining. Formal holiday meals are a breeze as there is plenty of space for a large table. The light filled great room features  a wall of  windows with motorized shades. Enjoy your morning coffee or an afternoon happy hour on the spacious covered deck. A covered front porch welcomes guests as they arrive. There is a guest room and full bathroom on this main level, ideal for a home office. Gleaming hardwood floors and an artistic curved stairway adorn the main level and lead to the upper bedroom suites. Laundry is conveniently tucked away, adjacent to the bedrooms. Spacious owner's suite has a custom oversized closet and a spa bathroom. Parking is easy at Easy Pines! 2 car garage, plus 2 more cars can fit on the driveway and there are several spaces on the private drive behind the garage. This home is custom, high end and unique. Be prepared to LOVE WHERE YOU LIVE!
